<h2><a name="isdigit" id="isdigit">isdigit</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Składnia:
</p>
<pre class="c code c++" style="font-family:monospace;">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cctype&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">int</span> isdigit<span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="kw4">int</span> ch<span class="br0">&#41;</span>;</pre>
<p>

Funkcja isdigit() zwraca wartość różną od zera jeżeli <em>ch</em> jest znakiem pomiędzy <em>&#039;0&#039;</em> i <em>&#039;9&#039;</em>. W przeciwnym wypadku funkcja zwraca <em>0</em>. Przykład:
</p>
<pre class="c code c++" style="font-family:monospace;">    <span class="kw4">char</span> c;
    scanf<span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="st0">&quot;%c&quot;</span><span class="sy0">,</span> <span class="sy0">&amp;</span>c<span class="br0">&#41;</span>;
&nbsp;
    <span class="kw1">if</span> <span class="br0">&#40;</span>isdigit<span class="br0">&#40;</span>c<span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="br0">&#41;</span>
        <a href="http://www.opengroup.org/onlinepubs/009695399/functions/printf.html"><span class="kw3">printf</span></a><span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="st0">&quot;Wprowadziles cyfre: %c<span class="es0">\n</span>&quot;</span><span class="sy0">,</span> c<span class="br0">&#41;</span>;</pre>
<p>
Tematy pokrewne: <a href="http://www.cppreference.com/wiki/pl/c/string/isalnum" class="wikilink2" title="pl:c:string:isalnum" rel="nofollow">isalnum</a>, <a href="http://www.cppreference.com/wiki/pl/c/string/isalpha" class="wikilink2" title="pl:c:string:isalpha" rel="nofollow">isalpha</a>, <a href="http://www.cppreference.com/wiki/pl/c/string/iscntrl" class="wikilink2" title="pl:c:string:iscntrl" rel="nofollow">iscntrl</a>, <a href="http://www.cppreference.com/wiki/pl/c/string/isgraph" class="wikilink2" title="pl:c:string:isgraph" rel="nofollow">isgraph</a>, <a href="http://www.cppreference.com/wiki/pl/c/string/isprint" class="wikilink2" title="pl:c:string:isprint" rel="nofollow">isprint</a>, <a href="http://www.cppreference.com/wiki/pl/c/string/ispunct" class="wikilink2" title="pl:c:string:ispunct" rel="nofollow">ispunct</a>, <a href="http://www.cppreference.com/wiki/pl/c/string/isspace" class="wikilink2" title="pl:c:string:isspace" rel="nofollow">isspace</a>, <a href="http://www.cppreference.com/wiki/pl/c/string/isxdigit" class="wikilink2" title="pl:c:string:isxdigit" rel="nofollow">isxdigit</a>
</p>

